{"m": 101, "et": "11:11", "spot": 7553.31, "action": "enter_short", "why": "Positive-gamma range day; price failed a 2nd probe at the highs (7556) BELOW an overwhelming, still-growing 7585 PIKA king ceiling (+21.6M, 15m +8.9) \u2014 dealers selling rips, rejecting price before it can even tap the pika. Floor collapsed (7500 +4.4M, 15m -4.8) = open downside air pocket. Massive barn fuel below (7560 -23.4M, 7550 -18.7M) accelerates the drop. Overshoot to day-high stalling = neg-gamma overshoot-stall entry. Rug thesis: reject at ceiling + barn-fueled acceleration into weak floor. Target node-to-node 7545->7535->7520/7510; stop break-and-hold above 7562."}
